  "detailed_description": "SIHEYUAN is a single and local co-op action-puzzle game of few words, but lots of tiles. Move the falling blocks, pass them and pass them again to fill the grid, in this minimalistic test of coordination for 1-4 players of any age, inspired by the tradition of \"siheyuan\", historical courtyards of Beijing, China.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239360/extras/2f09e28b8d8fdc38c3e04579137da083.poster.avif?t=1737107627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239360/extras/2f09e28b8d8fdc38c3e04579137da083.webm?t=1737107627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Juggle tiles between the 4 game areas in single-player mode, or pass them to your friends in multiplayer mode (up to 4P), talking, collaborating, and sharing (or shouting) your strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239360/extras/9999324ed68bb2eb876665bac32c5993.poster.avif?t=1737107627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239360/extras/9999324ed68bb2eb876665bac32c5993.webm?t=1737107627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>• 13 different levels to unlock<br>• 13 special modifiers, changing the game's pace from meditative to hectic<br>• Unique minimalistic abstract design inspired by Chinese traditional architecture, color theory, opera, and games.",
  "about_the_game": "SIHEYUAN is a single and local co-op action-puzzle game of few words, but lots of tiles. Move the falling blocks, pass them and pass them again to fill the grid, in this minimalistic test of coordination for 1-4 players of any age, inspired by the tradition of \"siheyuan\", historical courtyards of Beijing, China.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239360/extras/2f09e28b8d8fdc38c3e04579137da083.poster.avif?t=1737107627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239360/extras/2f09e28b8d8fdc38c3e04579137da083.webm?t=1737107627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Juggle tiles between the 4 game areas in single-player mode, or pass them to your friends in multiplayer mode (up to 4P), talking, collaborating, and sharing (or shouting) your strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239360/extras/9999324ed68bb2eb876665bac32c5993.poster.avif?t=1737107627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239360/extras/9999324ed68bb2eb876665bac32c5993.webm?t=1737107627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>• 13 different levels to unlock<br>• 13 special modifiers, changing the game's pace from meditative to hectic<br>• Unique minimalistic abstract design inspired by Chinese traditional architecture, color theory, opera, and games.",
